{"tid":1319984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點解 我覺得唔好對無綫前線記者郁手","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:51:03.000Z","uid":66390,"like":10,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11b7db2d2269896f86e0eee3d1225171c4d0b593","tid":1319984,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"我預左多負評 但我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得<br />\n1. 屌尻佢地<br />\n2. 遮鏡頭 / 圍住佢地 / 叫觀眾轉台<br />\n3. 搞尻佢地架車<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係可以既</span><br />\n<br />\n但講到動手打佢地 我覺得有少少over左<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地前線未至於去到黑警咁撚樣<br />\n無禮 動手 偏一邊攝錄<br />\n<br />\n其實身為傳媒<br />\n確係有責任記錄每一個場面<br />\n再交上去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（不過前線明知高層會偏頗報道 就應該避免一啲鏡頭）</span><br />\n<br />\n我地的確有用武力 怕咩認<br />\n唔需要塑造到示威者係綿羊咁<br />\n大家就係支持以暴易暴 <br />\n<br />\n點解要用武力打差佬？<br />\n因為黑警濫用暴力 所以我地要求對等武力 <br />\n同埋予以還擊<br />\n<br />\n我唔會講咩係無綫高層衰個啲閪野<br />\n但我地都應該予以對等方式對待無綫前線記者<br />\n<br />\n示威者只係遮CCTVB鏡頭 圍佢地 <br />\n已經有足夠壓力 <br />\n無謂動手呀<br />\n<br />\n6.28 將軍澳見啦"},{"pid":"deafc80969c5364d3e9c1da1790b0a9fb5b8f860","tid":1319984,"uid":212119,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"都冇人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca661a0d411f63fe0602b0e2dc76174018103d6e","tid":1319984,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"deafc80969c5364d3e9c1da1790b0a9fb5b8f860","tid":1319984,"uid":212119,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"都冇人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"上水個陣有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b671c3a07cd3e795529f41ca99453d24e40512c3","tid":1319984,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/328RYOa.png\" d